description: Cansortium Inc., through its subsidiaries, produces and sells medical cannabis in the United States. The company engages in the cultivation, processing, retail, and distribution activities. Its medical cannabis products are offered in oral drops, capsules, suppositories, topicals, syringes, dried flower, prerolls, cartridges, and edibles. The company provides its products under the Fluent brand name. As of August 20, 2021, it operated 28 dispensaries. Cansortium Inc. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Miami, Florida.
